           05  WS-DB-USER-TERM     PIC X VALUE X'00'.
       01  WS-DB-PASSWORD.
           05  WS-DB-PASSWORD-TEXT PIC X(9) VALUE 'CARBONPWD'.
           05  WS-DB-PASSWORD-TERM PIC X VALUE X'00'.
       01  WS-DB-NAME-LEN         PIC S9(4) COMP-5 VALUE 13.
